one_reviews_text:
The game starts great. All tasks can be performed with an ultra light plane. I have some real world flying experience. I only miss a variometer, because it is not easy to see how quick you climb/dive in VR.
But then you buy a glider with a rocket. Sorry, but for me it is impossible to perform tasks with a glider with a rocket motor with a few bursts of power. And I cannot earn more money with the ultra light, so it looks like it is end of game for me.

@Developer: Thank you for the response. I want to use all the airports and planes, so I used Artmoney money cheat to increase my money. No I can fly all the planes and use all the airbases and do all the tasks! I just want to fly and do tasks and bypass the glider problem. I upgraded the experience from 3 to 4.

You do get the sense of flying, is it thrilling, no, these are gliders, they only have so much speed.  It was a lot of fun flying through the cliffs, banking left and right to avoid the sides of the cliffs.  

My only complaint is I would like more a variety of jobs.  Maybe delivering parcels from one airport to another with limited fuel and time, or more challanging rings (through the cliffs would be nice).

@Developer...No I haven't yet
